{
  "stem": "3453.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We heard some news penetrated in little-- little cut-outs from the newspapers, what they-- they-- for the [? populace, ?] not for the ghetto people, for the population outside.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They are transferring Jews from this and this town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we find out that there is-- was already transferring Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's a bad news.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's-- they are killing them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They are doing something with them, and we could not figure out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we knew that something horrible things are happening.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Next, our ghetto was surrounded one night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what-- right away a decree, right in the [? thing, ?] a big placard, a placard came.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was written right in the-- on the front of the municipality that the-- all the [? populace ?] of the ghetto must come to the gate, to the square, where the gate was the next day.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Our ghetto was surrounded with-- with Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The-- not the-- the Ukrainians who were helping the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were Nazis just as much, and Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And on that day, people start-- we saw it's a panic, a panic right away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Women with children start running from street to street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they used to-- just spiteful, they used to throw in-- used to with-- with real live ammunition, they used to throw 'em into the crowd.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And some of them were killed right there and then.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my mother, right away we were-- we were a little bit away from the-- from the main crowd.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My mother insisted I should go into hiding.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I didn't want to.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But she absolutely insisted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I decided to go into hiding.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She said, maybe-- maybe some of-- maybe one of us will survive or something, whatever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Go into hiding.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the hiding place was at my uncle's house.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
